Tips for avoiding procrastination:
1) Make a list of big or small task and ask yourself why are you procrastinating
2) Use evernote or other app and get organized
3) Develop a habit of reading certain amount of pages a day
4) Break things down into small tasks and go step by step
5) Avoid doing errands like checking email, etc.
6) Don't spend too much time planning.



Solution:
